{"tid":2430453,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男生襲警原判感化 律政司覆核得直 上訴庭改判更生中心","createTime":"2021-03-03T02:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T03:49:59.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"185955eecd8c16a89b1f1dfb2b2a1a890716c940","tid":2430453,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14097&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiurZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=205e5c6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14097</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第二十八庭  <br />\n#潘兆初高等法院首席法官<br />\n#彭偉昌上訴庭法官<br />\n#陳慶偉法官<br />\n#刑期覆核<br />\n#20200119旺角<br />\n<br />\n陳（17）<br />\n<br />\n案情：於2020年1月19日在旺角登打士街43A號外襲擊警員X。據悉，答辯人企圖以磚頭投擲警員。認罪後，嚴舜儀主任裁判官判處答辯人12個月感化令。<br />\n<br />\n🔴速報：改判更生中心🔴<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"7b289b14d3c33fd8b7e489a24837276a83c75156","tid":2430453,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded31088d768672f53311844b348d8f02e1384b9","tid":2430453,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8297b470232493e6be5224812de382eff1bb5c","tid":2430453,"uid":20291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:57:20.000Z","msg":"其實有邊次係上訴失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa40caf6f8c6e3408f0d435ac92e9704669b98f","tid":2430453,"uid":177168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:57:40.000Z","msg":"都叫咗判完即刻飛啦"},{"pid":"c55a72de36801c38bc1d72a0bff939d2db5e94e5","tid":2430453,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:58:42.000Z","msg":"司法迫害加監庭"},{"pid":"795aab98d4e6cd81073a5f5c26df736b8d88a9ef","tid":2430453,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:07:58.000Z","msg":"律政司不服刑罰過輕申請刑期覆核，上訴庭裁定原審裁判官嚴舜儀原則性犯錯，刑罰顯然不足，撤銷原有的感化令，在細閱勞教和更生中心報告，以及被告的求情信後，終判被告入更生中心。書面理由將於下周五（3月12日）上午10時頒布。<br />\n<br />\n首席法官潘兆初指，勞教中心報告顯示被告的健康情況不適合入勞教中心，更生中心則指被告身心均適合入更生中心，被告在求情信亦表示有悔意，希望上訴庭維持原判。但上訴庭考慮所有報告、求情信、代表律師早前陳詞後，認為判入更生中心最為合適。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告在案發當晚身穿全黑裝束及戴面罩，在示威者堵路地點附近遊蕩，手持磚頭不斷粗言向警員叫罵。警員X截停被告時，被告用磚打X左手及推其心口，致其左手腫脹瘀傷，後被4警員合力制服並拘捕，帶返警署。原審裁判官嚴舜儀考慮被告年輕初犯及坦白認罪，醫療報告亦指被告確診自閉症，記憶力衰退，難以集中，容易暈眩，去年9月判被告12個月感化令。"},{"pid":"b76691e2aebc5d55668bbf5acb6d34d00bd467e4","tid":2430453,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f87f38d116ee2e8ed6dff5b3854599a4c75a09","tid":2430453,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:30:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74f86e044845c30cdc794c1041fc080f1fcade7","tid":2430453,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:32:58.000Z","msg":"阿叻:全部都依足基本法例辦事<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2429300\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2429300</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qigvxv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qigvxv.png&h=13fe40f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1d8mEa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1d8mEa.png&h=6d4ebe9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6bMehcv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6bMehcv.png&h=57363147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MB7QzZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMB7QzZa.png&h=c066bc7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cHEWvxv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcHEWvxv.png&h=1c4750b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cc9257b067adde886ba0264c0f0a5716dc880b4","tid":2430453,"uid":136994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6546e2d9eb24f6b95bebb929388ac4cdd5adb7b","tid":2430453,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}